name: Plutus SYK
description: PlutusDAO provides liquidity in many forms. Our main products are and have been Liquid staking derivatives, plsASSETs. Plutus SYK (plsSYK), specifically, is a plsASSET that provides a liquid staking option for Stryke's xSYK - a gauge controlling and yield bearing version of their Stryke token, SYK. With plsSYK you can enjoy 88% of the underlying yield of xSYK, plus a protocol owned compounding part, while staying liquid. There is a plsSYK/SYK -pool that Plutus buys back from and compounds yield.
